[Optimizing Gaia]= life optimizes the physical and chemical environment to best meet the biosphere needs.
 =(translated) = biosphere(life) optimizes the global environment to best meet the biosphere needs.
[Homeostatic Gaia]= holds that athmsophere-biosphere interactions are dominated by negative feedbacks (and this feedback hepls to stabilize the global environment)






//(global) Environment = globale Umwelt = Die Umgebung eines Lebewesens, die auf dieses einwirkt und seine Lebensumstände beeinflusst = Biosphäre & Athmosphäre
// physical and chemical environment = biological, physical and chemical environment = global environment